            We glad to introduce ourselves as the manufacturers & exporters of all kinds of Forgings. We belong to well reputed "Kishan” group of Rajkot. We are having proud-mark of ISO-9001:2008 from TUV. Ours' is a sister concern of M/s. Kishan Auto parts Limited, the leading manufacturers & exporters of Connecting Rods in India.
